  (2)   Paragraph (1)(A) and (B), "or" deleted and punctuation changed;
  (3)   Paragraph (1)(C), punctuation changed; and
  (4)   Paragraph (4), (A) and (B) reformatted as subparagraphs (A) and (B) and punctuation changed.
